---
---
<section class="relative min-h-[100vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-end px-6 pt-32 pb-32 overflow-hidden bg-brand-bg">
  <video
    autoplay
    loop
    muted
    playsinline
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover -z-10 opacity-60"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <source src="/videos/7DBMcn5jb3MWPbWNhMj0lM8045E.webm" type="video/webm" />
  </video>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10"
    style="background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(252,102,48,0.25), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 80%, rgba(0,91,255,0.18), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,13,13,0.4) 0%, rgba(13,13,13,0.95) 100%);"
  />

  <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="font-medium leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.025em] text-[44px] md:text-[72px] lg:text-[96px] text-brand-fg">
      The Open and<br/>Borderless AI Network
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed tracking-[0.01em] text-brand-fg/85">
      The Internet made information open &amp; borderless. Bitcoin made money open &amp; borderless.
      OpenxAI makes intelligence open &amp; borderless.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <a
        href="https://studio.openxai.org"
        class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-brand-fg text-brand-bg font-semibold hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors"
      >
        Launch Now
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://medium.com/openxai"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full border border-white/25 text-brand-fg/95 font-medium hover:border-white/40 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"
      >
        Read full vision &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
